    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1928-03-14T15:10:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1928-03-07T17:00:00-05:00" n="296"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d296">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">881.00/1385: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Herrick</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName> [<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1928-03-14T15:10:00-05:00"
                            notBefore="1928-03-07T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">undated</hi>
                        </date>].<lb/>[Received March 14, 1928—3:10 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>67. Foreign Office informs me that four-power Tangier conversations will begin at
                    Quai d’Orsay on March 20th. See my despatch No. 8400 of March 6.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herrick</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
